# - Try to find Calligra Libraries
# Once done this will define
#
#  CALLIGRALIBS_FOUND - system has Calligra
#  CALLIGRALIBS_INCLUDE_DIR - the Calligra include directory
# KOMAIN_LIBRARY
# KOTEXT_LIBRARY
# KOODF_LIBRARY
# KOPAGEAPP_LIBRARY
# KOKROSS_LIBRARY
